/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實一早就應該裁警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加上向來都有邊界巡邏隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本唔使咁多一車車成隊差佬通街行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現實個治安風險一來冇以前咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二來啲配套同後援都進化晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係要咁多人手？隔幾條街一隊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知移交前有冇傾過警力問題<br />\n將個警力都高嘅地方交畀個極權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n絕對有一日拎出嚟用<br />\n（而家用緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0de8c3f4313949937d65715e8e444a819ab1bd","tid":2217773,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T17:36:53.000Z","msg":"芬蘭有身份證的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"df9b592a821ee49b5c7960ab8d7551f27b20d9f7","tid":2217773,"uid":1249,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T16:44:29.000Z","msg":"想問下有冇人係同我一樣唔知道㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}